data.description: Seller offering up to $8,000 towards buyer's closing costs, prepaid and / or rate buydown! Charming three-bedroom, two-bathroom residence with a two-car garage and a pool. This delightful home is situated in the heart of Kissimmee, offering convenient access to entertainment, shopping centers, and a variety of restaurants. You'll also find major highways like I4, the FL Turnpike, 429, and the 417 just a short drive away, making it easy to reach Disney Parks and the Orlando International Airport. The home boasts a well-designed split floor plan and elegant vaulted ceilings. Most of the flooring throughout the house is tiled, with the exception of the third bedroom, which features cozy carpeting. Located in the Windward Cay Community, this property provides straightforward access to 192 and allows for short-term rentals. The community primarily consists of owner-occupied homes, with a few dedicated to vacation rentals. The spacious pool deck area is perfect for entertaining and hosting gatherings, and the pool itself is screened-in for added convenience. The roof was replaced in 2021, and the master bedroom and master bathroom offer direct access to the pool area. The interior and exterior of the home have recently been refreshed with a new coat of paint. Don't miss out on this wonderful opportunity – call now to schedule your appointment!
